high_descs: Turn around and take two steps then turn left and walk to the left side of the tub.
Pick up the sponge that's in front of you in the tub.
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the sink.
Get the sponge wet in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Take a step to your left.
Put the sponge on the edge of the counter to the right of the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet sponge on the counter.

high_descs: turn around and walk over to the bath tub on the left side of the room
grab the sponge out of the bath tub
turn left and walk over to the sink on the left side of the room
place the sponge inside of the sink, rinse it off, then take it back out
move to the left a bit and face the sink again
place the clean sponge on top of the sink
anns.task_desc: place a clean sponge on top of the sink counter

high_descs: Turn right and slightly right to the tub.
Take the sponge out of the tub.
Turn around and walk to the right sink.
Wash the sponge in the sink.
Place the sponge on the counter in between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean sponge on a counter.
